      'Includes: 120 components across 8 categories, both theme variants, a Figma variables setup for quick rebranding, and lifetime update access. Licensed for commercial use on unlimited client projects.',
    ],
    topics: ['The Product', 'The Problem It Solves', "What's Included"],
  },
  {
    id:       'nightfall',
    category: 'PRODUCT',
    title:    'Nightfall',
    meta:     '$39 · Includes 6 page templates',
    body: [
      'Nightfall is a dark-mode Astro starter theme — six page templates (landing, blog index, article, pricing, about, contact) built on the same cascade-layer CSS architecture this site uses, no Tailwind or CSS-in-JS dependency.',
      'Built for developers who want a real starting codebase, not a Figma file to translate themselves. "A freelance developer who wants a production-ready Astro base instead of starting from a blank astro.config" is the specific buyer this serves.',
      'Fully plug-and-play: clone, `npm install`, `npm run dev`. Comes with a documented content-collection schema for the blog templates and a short setup guide — no configuration required to see it running.',
    ],
    topics: ['The Format', 'The Buyer', 'The Onboarding'],
