  {
    id:       'glyphset',
    category: 'PRODUCT',
    title:    'Glyphset',
    meta:     '$19 · 200 icons included',
    body: [
      'Glyphset is a 200-icon set drawn at a single consistent stroke weight and corner radius — SVG, PNG, and an Astro-ready icon-component wrapper included, built to solve the specific annoyance of mixing icon packs from three different sources and having nothing visually match.',
      'The differentiator against the many free icon packs already out there: every icon in this set was drawn by hand for this specific stroke system, not auto-generated or assembled from mismatched sources — visual consistency across all 200 is the entire pitch.',
      'Licensed for commercial use, including client projects and products you resell, with no attribution required. An extended licence for icon-pack resale specifically is available on request.',
